Module LAB_02
Package ki304.salahub.Lab2

Class Scaner

java.lang.Object
ki304.salahub.Lab2.Scaner
public class Scaner extends Object
The `Scaner` class represents a scanner with various properties and functionalities. It includes information about dimensions, properties, connections, and functionality. This class provides methods to retrieve information, control power, clean the buffer, and perform scanning operations.
Since:
2023-11-16
Version:
1.0
Author:
